FT  21 SEP 93 / World Trade News: ABB in power parts venture with Russia
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By ANDREW BAXTER
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
ASEA BROWN BOVERI, the Swiss-Swedish engineering group, is forming a joint
