FT  20 SEP 93 / International Company News: Mid-Ocean - Correction
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A table in the Financial Times on September 15 stated that Mid-Ocean, the
Bermuda-based reinsurance company, raised Dollars 250m in new capital during
1993. Mid-Ocean has raised Dollars 325m this year bringing its total capital
base (including retained earnings) to some Dollars 735m.
